Exclusive offer from The Lancet Infectious Diseases: free 2-week online trial ****starting 14 Mar 2012****
----------------------------------------------------------------------
You may know of our reputation for publishing only the most important and ground-breaking research and reviews? Maybe you recognize us as the infectious diseases journal with the top ranked Impact Factor? Or, possibly you have seen the print journal on your colleague's desk and wanted to know more?

Now is your chance to get to know us better!

Get the best in infectious disease with our free 2-week online trial.
Click here:
http://www.bitly.com/Free_TLID_Trial

Sign up today for a free online trial to The Lancet Infectious Diseases and receive 2-weeks unlimited access to all the content the leading journal in infectious diseases has to offer including:
- important original research and review articles published back to our 1st issue in 2001;
- advance notification of our Online First publication of fast-tracked original research;
- comprehensive and unbiased editorial insights and commentary across infectious disease medicine

Don't wait! The trial starts 14 Mar 2012 and ends 28 Mar 2012!
Click here:
http://www.bitly.com/Free_TLID_Trial

Visit http://www.bitly.com/Free_TLID_Trial and enter promotion code PA195.

Don't delay, online trial access expires on 28 Mar 2012!

Want to see a sample?

